This paper deals with the optimization of neural networks, which is a common topic in the field of computational neuroscience and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the use of metaheuristics, which is a subfield of optimization algorithms commonly used in machine learning. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with classification accuracy, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
